  "linked_names": [],
  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "A sudden insight : unlike all other creatures (e.g. humans) _Valis does not move along any of the 3 spacial axes_; its only motion is along the temporal axis which, for it, is totally accretional : a laying down of layers in terms of developing forms (the only one it disclosed to me is the pretty girl wearing the fish necklace, but that is enough to give me the idea).\n\nA layer is laid down; then years pass, which is for Valis a pause. Then the next layer, perhaps years later, is laid down direct",
      "matched_alias": "Judaism",
